* {{audio|en-us-ablaze.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Adjective===
{{en-adj}}

# On fire; in a blaze, [[gleaming]].
#: ''All '''ablaze''' with crimson and gold.''  -[[w:Henry Wadsworth Longfellow|Henry Wadsworth Longfellow]]
# In a state of [[glowing]] excitement or ardent desire.
#: ''The young Cambridge democrats were all '''ablaze''' to assist Torrijos.''  -[[w:Thomas Carlyle|Thomas Carlyle]]

